{"tid":1069479,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)魔戒三部曲","createTime":"2019-03-20T04:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T11:39:15.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25499c3ca94400dd81fa1dbc14c1999001a2fec3","tid":1069479,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9JBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=05b5cb70\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9JBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=938a86e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9JBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=feb19d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n1.凱蘭崔爾敍述的序言講及索倫鑄造至尊魔戒以圖征服中土大陸，人類及精靈組成聯盟發動最後同盟戰役推翻了索倫。至尊魔戒落入埃西鐸手中。埃西鐸後來被半獸人所殺，至尊魔戒失落，在數千年後才被哈比人史麥戈所獲，因受魔戒的影響，史麥戈成為咕嚕。至尊魔戒急欲返回它的主人索倫手裡，於是離棄咕嚕，被哈比人比爾博&middot;巴金斯所獲。<br />\n在比爾博111歲生日當天，比爾博將至尊魔戒讓給堂姪佛羅多&middot;巴金斯。比爾博好友甘道夫經過探查後發現那就是失落的至尊魔戒，由於索倫急欲取得至尊魔戒，甘道夫囑咐佛羅多要儘速帶同魔戒離開夏爾。甘道夫趕往艾辛格與巫師的首領薩魯曼商討對策，薩魯曼透露索倫已派出戒靈奪取魔戒，認為中土自由子民無從抵抗，並邀請甘道夫和他一起加入索倫陣營。甘道夫拒絕，薩魯曼遂將甘道夫囚禁在歐散克塔<br />\n<br />\n2.電影開首呼應首部曲，甘道夫在摩瑞亞的橋上與炎魔對峙，甘道夫與炎魔墜落深淵。佛羅多從夢境中醒過來，與山姆繼續行程，他們被希望奪回魔戒的咕嚕襲擊，佛羅多及山姆制伏了他，佛羅多正需要一名嚮導引領他們前往魔多，於是讓他引路。<br />\n在洛汗，薩魯曼那一支擄走梅里及皮聘的強獸人橫過草原向艾辛格進發，勒苟拉斯、金靂及亞拉岡尾隨追蹤。薩魯曼亦在洛汗國王身邊安插了葛力馬&middot;巧言控制著希優頓。薩魯曼聚集大軍展開攻勢，沿途燒殺破壞，希優頓的兒子希優德戰死。希優頓之甥伊歐墨責難葛力馬，反被葛力馬驅逐，伊歐墨聚集了一些忠實的部下離去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.電影開始時講述哈比人德戈及史麥戈發現魔戒的過程，史麥戈殺死德戈並奪取魔戒，從此隱匿深山裡。<br />\n返回現在，亞拉岡等人來到艾辛格，會合梅里及皮聘，薩魯曼想告知甘道夫魔多的事情時，被葛力馬‧巧言從後偷襲，跌下塔底死亡，真知晶球從袍內流出，皮聘拾起了薩魯曼的真知晶球，但被甘道夫取去。希優頓在返回伊多拉斯後舉行慶典。佛羅多等人逐漸靠近魔多，咕嚕的陰謀面也逐漸呈現，他計劃引導哈比人到西力斯昂哥，讓屍羅殺死他們，他便可獲得魔戒，又開始離間佛羅多與山姆<br />\n<br />\n1 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9JBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=e064867c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9JBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=565dfcc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f39898a29eadfcd4515c07e0188917987fad37","tid":1069479,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"改12 30"},{"pid":"cdf63644fc3c79c8c0927414de3948c9013e6d7d","tid":1069479,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/Ringstrilogyposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedi